artificialFastqGenerator

Class Read

  • java.lang.Object
    • artificialFastqGenerator.AbstractRead
      • artificialFastqGenerator.Read

  • public class Read
extends AbstractRead
    An instance of this class corresponds to a read in an artificial fastq file. It has fields for its Nucleobase sequence, unique integer ID, the other read in the pair, its encoded quality scores, and the genotypes which actually get read (i.e. may contain error).
